She's Trapped In A Haunted Hospital | Room 6 | Christine Taylor | Thriller Movie

Amy's boyfriend is injured in a car crash and taken to a hospital that no longer exists. There, Amy and a concerned stranger enter a nightmare where demons walk among us, hallucinations run rampant, and sultry nurses engage in lesbian blood rites.

2006 | Stars: Christine Taylor, Shane Brolly, Jerry O'Connell
